SetAttestor_Integration_Test
├── when caller not comptroller or admin
│  └── it should revert
├── when caller comptroller
│  ├── given attestor already set by admin
│  │  └── it should revert
│  └── given attestor not set by admin
│     └── it should set the attestor
└── when caller campaign creator
   ├── it should set the attestor
   └── it should mark attestorSetByAdmin as true
